    "body": "The error was `fatal error: runtime: out of memory` at the end of DAG generation.\n\nSince this was for a relatively old version (0.9.15 vs 0.9.22 today), can you re-run this with an updated docker container, ensuring it has at least 2GB memory? DAG should be about 1GB right now in addition to whatever geth consumes.\n",
